# Staff — Management Endpoints
# UC-028 (invite), UC-029 (deactivate), UC-030 (update profile), UC-031 (activate), list, detail
# TenantContext is populated from X-Tenant-ID / X-Actor-ID headers (set by BFF).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}
@staffId = {{staffWorkerId}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — list staff
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all staff for the tenant (default limit=50, offset=0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### List staff with explicit pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff?limit=10&offset=0
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — me/tenants (UC-022 switch-staff-tenant)
# Returns all tenants the authenticated staff account is registered at.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get all tenants for the currently authenticated staff member
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/me/tenants
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — me/status (BFF's ActiveStaffGuard self-check, TD23 Story 11)
# Self-service isActive check — target is always RequestContext.actorId, never a URL param.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get the currently authenticated staff member's own active status (MANAGER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/me/status
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### Get the currently authenticated staff member's own active status (STAFF, non-manager)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/me/status
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{staffWorkerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: STAFF

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — get staff by id
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get a specific staff member by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{staffId}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — invite (UC-028)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Invite a new STAFF member
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/invite
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "email": "novo@lavacar.com.br",
  "firstName": "João",
  "lastName": "Silva",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

###

### Invite a new MANAGER
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/invite
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "email": "gerente2@lavacar.com.br",
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Costa",
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — update profile (UC-030)
# email is never editable — it's the lookup key used on every staff Google login.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Update a staff member's name and role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{staffId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "João Silva Editado",
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — deactivate (UC-029)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Deactivate a STAFF member
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{staffId}}/deactivate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — activate (UC-031)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Reactivate a deactivated STAFF member
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{staffId}}/activate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### 400 — Missing X-Tenant-ID header
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff

###

### 404 — Staff id not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000009999
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 409 — Email already active in same tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/invite
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "email": "gerente@lavacar.com.br",
  "firstName": "João",
  "lastName": "Silva",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

###

### 403 — Self-deactivation attempt
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{managerId}}/deactivate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 409 — Last active manager (deactivate)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{managerId}}/deactivate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: 99999999-0000-4000-8000-000000000001
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 400 — Update with empty name
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{staffId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

###

### 403 — Self-reactivation attempt
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{managerId}}/activate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 409 — Already-active member reactivation attempt
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{staffId}}/activate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 409 — Update demoting the last active manager to STAFF
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/{{managerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: 99999999-0000-4000-8000-000000000001
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "Gerente",
  "role": "STAFF"
}
